.SH NAME
batadv_get_hardif_from_info \- Retrieve hardif from genl attributes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct batadv_hard_iface *" batadv_get_hardif_from_info
.BI "(struct batadv_priv *bat_priv "  ","
.BI "struct net *net "  ","
.BI "struct genl_info *info "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bat_priv" 12
the bat priv with all the soft interface information
.IP "net" 12
the applicable net namespace
.IP "info" 12
receiver information
.SH "RETURN"
Pointer to hard interface (with increased refcnt) on success, error
pointer on error
